beginning, containing an area of ONE THOUSAND TWO HUNDRED FORTY SIX (1,246) SQUARE METERS . All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by PS. cyl. conc. Mons., 15 x 60 cm., except points 7 to 9 by Old PS. Cyl. Conc. Mons., 15 x 60 cm., bearings true, date of original survey, during 1907 (Muntinlupa Estate) that of the subdivision survey on January 15–20, 1991. Approved on June 27, 1991.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 13 th day of JAN, in the year of Our Lord, two thousand and three.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

